，根據澳門博彩業顧問公司，本月首１２日的博彩收入為９３﹒５億澳門元，按年升２０％至２２％。　　瑞信指，估計本月至今行業ＶＩＰ賭收按年升３０％至４０％，而中場賭收最多按年升１０％至１２％，主要由高端需求帶動。該行認為，颱風損毀及負面因素消除幫助澳門表現改善。　　瑞信表示，整體而言，中場博彩收入仍看到持續改善，行業估值合理於２０１８年ＥＢＩＴＤＡ１４倍水平。　　該行指，澳門博彩收入的強勁勢頭、市場看漲的情緒及市場對今年第四季及明年的博彩收入的預期較低，將會有助支持行業股價。　　瑞信表示，繼續看好銀河娛樂（０００２７）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9200a644ba2b9bb62dc9f8d33b4648ec9113cce6","tid":453232,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"賭股又準備爆發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c8a04327238bb89943e4b4935ab8c526fc9bbd","tid":453232,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"冇有手足同船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6fdbff9534543d45a31f2ea0dae445f0b5e8c4","tid":453232,"uid":134128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"點解簡銀河 而唔簡其他賭業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe6fba8c0745adfecf7b20c8bccb68e9935ca58","tid":453232,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"澳門派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d人拎去賭又會爆上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f39007934cc32228447faf56057042d44046c2","tid":453232,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解簡銀河 而唔簡其他賭業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀河多人炒 升得最靚<br />\n個人最睇好金沙 但弱勢升唔